description:
This is an album of music inpired by Touhou and/or remixes of the Touhou video game series.

This album contains the popular fan-hit "Night of Knights", along with other enjoyable songs across 4 discs.

The filenames have Japanese characters, but the file tags should all be the English translation of the title.
